junior.job_path_description: Start your cybersecurity journey with essential courses that cover secure software development, basic threat modeling, and security principles to prepare for an entry-level cybersecurity role.
junior.title: Cybersecurity Associate

medior.job_path_description: Build on foundational knowledge with mid-level training that includes threat modeling, infrastructure security, and DevSecOps practices to transition into more advanced roles.
medior.title: Cybersecurity Engineer

senior.job_path_description: Develop specialized knowledge in advanced threat defense, secure architecture design, and cloud-native security tools, preparing for senior roles in cybersecurity leadership.
senior.title: Senior Cybersecurity Architect
